---
title: Alfredo Style Cheesy Chicken Linguine with spinach, chives and balsamic glaze
description: Our twist on the famous pasta dish created in 1908 by an Italian restaurateur. This is a creamy cheesy recipe sprinkled with chives and filled with succulent chicken.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/HF_Y24_R25_W42_IE_IEQC28034-2_Main_17_R_high-197200ca.jpg
